rmal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2025都引到美國追住你黎打 華為被人打到半死  仲搞到2035出黎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T15:42:05.000Z","msg":"然後2021年仲未自煮研發到晶片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237779750a6c6cf42588a5cf8c5edee0af499b1c","tid":2400064,"uid":128514,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T15:51:45.000Z","msg":"一個連動物生命都唔尊重既國家，想擔大旗代表全球? 唔好笑大人個口吧!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210124/V3MYT6YG35BDTGSM4UITU67NTA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210124%2FV3MYT6YG35BDTGSM4UITU67NTA%2F&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMItKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=6f186eb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210124%2FV3MYT6YG35BDTGSM4UITU67NTA%2F&h=82250231\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210124/V3MYT6YG35BDTGSM4UITU67NTA/</a><br />\n<br />\n內地無良商人推「動物盲盒」 10蚊人仔抽哥基犬 動保人士鬧爆：人渣都不如<br />\n<br />\n（新增：內容）內地網絡經濟發達，衣食住行的商品都可以網購。但有無良商人竟然想到，以抽「盲盒」的形式出售寵物，最平僅需9.9元人民幣（下同，約11.8港元）就有機會獲得哥基、金毛尋回犬等名種狗或貓、烏龜、兔子。令人咋舌的是，這些活體盲盒竟有數千宗成交量，有香港動保人士向《蘋果》表示，擔心無良商人為求賺錢，薄利多銷，未來或會出現棄養潮。"},{"pid":"448fcba1526b76404e3f14d9367848272fa85343","tid":2400064,"uid":103146,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4461225a7320cb296c32d1683bbb845e0e398fd9","tid":2400064,"uid":255637,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2025都引到美國追住你黎打 華為被人打到半死  仲搞到2035出黎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T15:57:36.000Z","msg":"賊佬試沙煲<br />\n你喐手佢就退兩步，撞正對家綏善主義就會一路向前衝"},{"pid":"9ec5a15a63cc00b6827011